est to obtain the Rough Leather Sack on Kerra Isle near Toxxulia.  According to Everlore, this sack is No Drop/Lore, 6 slots, reduces weight 25%, and large items do not fit inside.<br>
I love the fact that some of the items for the quest are things I forage up and sell all the time.  Here is what is supposedly needed (I haven't done the quest yet myself):<br>
A bottle of Tunare's finest: Felwithe<br>
Handmade backpack:  by one of our guild's tailors<br>
Tea Leaves: Foraged in East Karana<br>
Thunderhoof mushrooms: Foraged in South Karana<br>
<br>
Turn the items in to Feskr Drinkwater who is located on the main island.  Go over the bridge, turn left and follow the curve of the island until you see a couple of docks on your left.  Enter the building to your right and go upstairs and Feskr is somewhere up there.  My guess is you should hail him first.<br>
<br>
I can't wait to get one of these.  As a little wood elf, I get encumbered so easily! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/ugillraen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gillraen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/8/01 8:59:37 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Weight reducing sack quest on Kerra Isle</span><hr size=1> Since my foraging skills exceeded 100, I have been able to forage thunderhoof mushrooms (South Karana) on a regular basis.  My few forays into East Karana have yielded the tea leaves as well; unfortunately, I sell these exotic food items as they bring in good money (for foraged food items).  I will start saving them now.  Also, I have also foraged Wild Cabbage (North Karana) and Surefall Sap (Qeynos Hills) so if anyone has need of these items, let me know and I will save them as well.<br>
<br>
Oh yes, I also foraged a Basilisk Egg during my first foray into Rathe Mountains.  Already sold, but does anyone know what these are used for?   <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fthecounciloftwilightfrm7.showMessage?topicID=4.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fthecounciloftwilightfrm7.emailToFriend?topicID=6.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fthecounciloftwilightfrm7.threadControl?topicID=6.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fthecounciloftwilightfrm7.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fthecounciloftwilightfrm7.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub25.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thecounciloftwilightfrm2">Character Bios<option value="thecounciloftwilightfrm1">Got news?<option value="thecounciloftwilightfrm12">Oake's Treehouse<option value="thecounciloftwilightfrm7">Quest Questions and Answers<option value="thecounciloftwilightfrm3">Stories<option value="thecounciloftwilightfrm8">Item and Equipment Grab Bag<option value="thecounciloftwilightfrm9">Dear Santa...<option value="thecounciloftwilightfrm6">Agendas, Plans, and Procedures!